[[zh:帮助翻译这个网站]]
[[ja:翻訳のヘルプ]]
[[es:AyudaTraducción]]
The wiki has a number of /known languages/. See TranslatingPages for some background.

Here's what to do if you want to translate a page such as our SandBox:

# Visit SandBox
# Scroll to the bottom and click the _Add Translation_ link
# Pick a language such as Deutsch (only languages without existing /translation links/ are offered...)
# Choose the name of the translated page name, eg. !SandKasten
# Click the '''Go!''' button
# This will add the /translation link/ %%[[de:SandKasten]]%% to the SandBox page, telling the wiki that !SandKasten is a translation of !SandBox
# You will end up editing the !SandKasten page
